{"tid":1692194,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(埋嚟睇)連登有愛會員引用哲人名句奉勸各位勿成怪物","createTime":"2019-11-04T03:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T11:32:20.000Z","uid":219269,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8e328154ebd96a6a8233b27a289ddf0ab14c3d90","tid":1692194,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:24:20.000Z","msg":"巴打佢有如螢火蟲一樣出現響我眼前<br />\n即使手足被斬亦冇令其信念動搖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qz1sB4F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqz1sB4F.png&h=31c437e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可惜一眾「怪物」並唔領情<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qOM4Eh1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqOM4Eh1.png&h=258e9850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>我唔反對唔打， 只係因為我見證過手足變左怪物。<br />\n<br />\n10月21日 我係旺角遊行，見到一班人沖去隧道位，有個廢老帶住一個小朋友破壞緊連儂牆，廢老企係隧道入面，手足就係外面扔野私了佢，廢老扔磚還手。<br />\n<br />\n無人去理企係格離既小朋友， 得我一個上前抱起個小朋友，然後企埋一邊。<br />\n個廢老見到我都無攻擊我，然後有手足連我都扔埋，嗌 屌你 老豆奶共做仔既預左啦， 唔洗還呀？ 咁<br />\n<br />\n無自己人幫我講過一句說話，直到有個男人黎到，接左我抱住個小朋友，我走左 都無人企出黎幫過我。 大家都掛住想私了個廢老。 <br />\n<br />\n我唔反對私了，都唔鍾意 討厭藍絲。 <br />\n但我都親眼見到，有手足會無視一個唔關事既小朋友，想去私了一個無負責任既藍絲廢老。 <br />\n<br />\n如果運動可以贏，核爆我都唔割。<br />\n但都請比我會依個機會提醒一各位同路人，請緊記我地既信念同目標 千祈唔好走火入魔。 記得我地既人性 我地唔係暴徒。Remember what we are.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇完咸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足變咗怪物佢都唔割<br />\n<br />\n你地究竟明唔明大陸人斬人係想直接斬死你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ampnkNV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ampnkNV</a><br />\n#36 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08n0cHM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08n0cHM.png&h=da84fb6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔少得嘅仲有一段內心剖白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可見佢並唔care鬥爭嘅輸贏<br />\n反而係心中嘅高尚情操會唔會被怪物染指<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb95eccb0d88016ca3c39265c61c76439c9a12bc","tid":1692194,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"屌開咗響愚樂台添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ace10bd95d29e58ef1141ad2ded5ce2633fdafa","tid":1692194,"uid":125911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb95eccb0d88016ca3c39265c61c76439c9a12bc","tid":1692194,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"屌開咗響愚樂台添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9156c168bc0085f5cded9cd33e61e13d3898839","tid":1692194,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:45:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87875d76474f69088dd528c55dc4bc245a64da7a","tid":1692194,"uid":23400,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:46:03.000Z","msg":"都發生咁多野，你仲可以咁得閒理手足點暴力法，你都好撚嘢，沈po啦"},{"pid":"2ecbf395484b532e4d63c619e5591952c7830df8","tid":1692194,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb95eccb0d88016ca3c39265c61c76439c9a12bc","tid":1692194,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"屌開咗響愚樂台添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:55:30.000Z","msg":"咪咁on9啦樓豬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔變怪物<br />\n就永遠都打唔低怪物 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<code>\n拉</code>"},{"pid":"2999b5157860c8ef76b756623d25af2086595ee7","tid":1692194,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:09:28.000Z","msg":"會思考嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87e867a771d21add547775149e896dde50779f7","tid":1692194,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:17:52.000Z","msg":"11月2同11月3之後，整理左少少資訊，得閒可以入黎一齊傾下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692149</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ac6a682e75894a78d3d7050c405dbdc8e978f1da","tid":1692194,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:32:20.000Z","msg":"會思考嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}